       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. INTCALC.
       AUTHOR. BANKING SYSTEMS.
       DATE-WRITTEN. 2024-01-15.
       
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       SOURCE-COMPUTER. IBM-370.
       OBJECT-COMPUTER. IBM-370.
       
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  ACCOUNT-RECORD.
           05  ACCOUNT-NUMBER      PIC 9(10).
           05  ACCOUNT-BALANCE     PIC 9(13)V99.
           05  INTEREST-RATE       PIC 9V9999.
           05  INTEREST-AMOUNT     PIC 9(13)V99.
       
       01  CALCULATION-FIELDS.
           05  DAILY-RATE          PIC 9V9999999.
           05  DAYS-IN-PERIOD      PIC 9(3).
           05  TEMP-AMOUNT         PIC 9(15)V99.
       
       77  WS-RESULT              PIC 9(13)V99.
       
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-LOGIC.
           ACCEPT ACCOUNT-NUMBER.
           ACCEPT ACCOUNT-BALANCE.
           ACCEPT INTEREST-RATE.
           ACCEPT DAYS-IN-PERIOD.
           
           PERFORM CALCULATE-INTEREST.
           
           DISPLAY "ACCOUNT: " ACCOUNT-NUMBER.
           DISPLAY "BALANCE: " ACCOUNT-BALANCE.
           DISPLAY "INTEREST: " INTEREST-AMOUNT.
           
           STOP RUN.
       
       CALCULATE-INTEREST.
           DIVIDE INTEREST-RATE BY 365 GIVING DAILY-RATE.
           MULTIPLY ACCOUNT-BALANCE BY DAILY-RATE 
               GIVING TEMP-AMOUNT.
           MULTIPLY TEMP-AMOUNT BY DAYS-IN-PERIOD 
               GIVING INTEREST-AMOUNT.
           ADD INTEREST-AMOUNT TO ACCOUNT-BALANCE.
